The Rathe <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ibelink>ibelink</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 129<br> <font color=#333333>(11/19/02 4:08:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7907.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   It's pretty simple...</span><hr size=1> Bring a group or 2, make sure you have a rogue (to lockpick). Clear to the top of the whole place and kill the final black reaver. Neh`Ashiir will pop on his corpse. <br>
She's really easy to kill, no tricks, just beat the bizatch down <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=napsilan>napsilan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#333333>(11/19/02 4:09:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7907.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: It's pretty simple...</span><hr size=1> there is a way to Gflux and CotH up instead of romping through the palace, but i don't know the details.  Not sure if you still need a rogue if you do it this way.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=knuklesninefingers>Knukles Ninefingers</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#333333>(11/19/02 4:35:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7907.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: It's pretty simple...</span><hr size=1> Make sure you have levitate on when you fight her, she will Gflux you over the side and you will die from the fall, she nailed our cleric like this once  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
